translations: n.产出，结局；效果（outcome 的复数）

sentences.sentence: All of these outcomes are linked to a lack of physical exercise.
sentences.translation: 所有这些后果都与缺乏体育锻炼有关。

sentences.sentence: Teachers imagine they will improve outcomes if they tailor their presentations to each student.
sentences.translation: 教师们认为，如果他们为每个学生量身定制他们的演示文稿，就会提高教学效果。

sentences.sentence: Four possible outcomes have been identified.
sentences.translation: 现已确定有四种可能的结果。
